text: Harry Skinner may refer to: *Harry Skinner (dancer), dancer with the Royal New Zealand Ballet *Harry Skinner (ethnologist) (1886–1978), New Zealand soldier, ethnologist, university lecturer, museum curator, and librarian *Harry Skinner (footballer) (fl. 1878–1902), English professional footballer *Harry Skinner (politician) (1855–1929), U.S. Representative from North Carolina ==See also== * Henry Skinner
